{"tid":2160640,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"當紅女偶像戴口罩自拍冇人認得？公開真實身份網民嚇呆","createTime":"2020-08-17T05:51:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T17:29:38.000Z","uid":16659,"like":19,"dislike":100,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"6c10dcc07f1ed631a1d0dec6cc7a66533eedfacc","tid":2160640,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:51:36.000Z","msg":"猜猜我是誰～<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情持續，為了保護自己保護別人，這半年多以來大家都每日口罩不離身。對於一些認人能力比較差的人來說，戴口罩絕對是一個惡夢。不過近日有一名當紅女偶像的自拍照，竟然成功令網民集體「臉盲」，開始了一輪「估人遊戲」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/08/20200817_en_%E5%AE%9A%E5%BB%B6_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F08%2F20200817_en_%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%25BB%25B6_4.jpg&h=b1cfa774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這位女偶像擁有一頭金色長髮加齊瀏海，戴着口罩也可以看得出是素顏，白滑的肌膚加上深邃的雙眼皮令人非常羨慕。不過這張自拍照卻意外引起網民激烈的討論，因為大家對她的真實身份都有不同的猜測。有人認為她是gu9udan的世正，也有人猜測是宇宙少女的Exy或者是才剛以金髮回歸的GFRIEND成員Yerin。<br />\n<br />\n事實上這位自拍的主角其實是TWICE的定延！可能因為自出道起定延就多以短髮示人，所以一時變成金長髮大家都未能適應，戴上口罩後就更難認出。<br />\n<br />\n當然粉絲還是可以一眼就知道她的真實身份，不過對於網民來說這答案就比較出乎意料之外。但知道答案後大家都可以很快就將兩者聯繫，目前定延仍然因手術而在靜養當中，不過在昨日就透過TWICE的官方IG上傳這張照片，並留下了「剪頭髮」的表情，未知是否借此機會一改新造型呢？"},{"pid":"7421f178189fc2cca7d703ab1afdd5f7f4445201","tid":2160640,"uid":16659,"like":12,"dislike":57,"score":-45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:51:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/08/20200817_en_%E5%AE%9A%E5%BB%B6_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F08%2F20200817_en_%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%25BB%25B6_3.jpg&h=bb0aae6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE IG圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/08/20200817_en_%E5%AE%9A%E5%BB%B6_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F08%2F20200817_en_%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%25BB%25B6_1.jpg&h=f92fa910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/08/20200817_en_%E5%AE%9A%E5%BB%B6_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F08%2F20200817_en_%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%25BB%25B6_2.jpg&h=77a0aef3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a68494f39038c01dfd8a89a7581b7561af5f30a","tid":2160640,"uid":229026,"like":24,"dislike":53,"score":-29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:52:09.000Z","msg":"嘩痴孖筋好靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f08cd48d93a2c5f99e0f245bf487fd63b8ba81","tid":2160640,"uid":38904,"like":29,"dislike":5,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:52:21.000Z","msg":"膠到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89266734d6d7fdce2e1f0a3ebfaab8841f00a11f","tid":2160640,"uid":314679,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:52:49.000Z","msg":"屌奶星長定世一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee36fa8d2a3b2a41877c364aa626cc2f9d8ea92","tid":2160640,"uid":47487,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:52:49.000Z","msg":"偽娘戴假髮扮女人?"},{"pid":"30a307f3580d93cf7b8d8c40517b8b75c5c26a9e","tid":2160640,"uid":68080,"like":163,"dislike":0,"score":163,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T05:54:10.000Z","msg":"我夠膽講印狗第一眼都認唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efbaa862c2ea3a2bf763b455a7d652950242c0ba","tid":2160640,"uid":261849,"like":3,"dislike":